{"tid":1758173,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"唔知點解今日冇人企喺度睇閘","createTime":"2019-11-27T01:48:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T16:39:16.000Z","uid":251732,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"59129af652fc4609b28e0c2a923a1780efd2fae7","tid":1758173,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T01:48:13.000Z","msg":"今朝遲到被迫搭黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過個大堂已經冇人再企喺度睇閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n 咁撚樣嘅情況， 甚至乎就咁喺黃色物件眼前強攻閘機都冇人出聲<br />\n係咪以為個區選贏咗就冇人再搞事跳閘？<br />\n<br />\n所以大家都唔好忘記 抗爭由生活做起<br />\n唔好畀我哋嘅血汗錢流入紅色資本手上<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e8183c4bc7d8e085a7b4abecca0da155770858e","tid":1758173,"uid":1477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T01:48:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/omEX1tT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FomEX1tT.jpg&h=57874f45&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PrdqqVy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPrdqqVy.jpg&h=1739302f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n怕香港人善忘嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n想聲援理大手足嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n和理非嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n勇武嘅，推行動 post 啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個係行動post，星期三晚，我地聚首商場，以和理非聲援理大手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1756593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1756593</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d8bae02c22fd79a065985a97bc3443543409fdb2","tid":1758173,"uid":94819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T01:48:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5a7511690328a6d26b1b9833ff1d2ba57da24144","tid":1758173,"uid":110125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59129af652fc4609b28e0c2a923a1780efd2fae7","tid":1758173,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTi